body_html:
I'm running Object Detection https://github.com/tensorflow/models/tree/master/research/object_detection

on ssd_inception_v2_coco model https://github.com/tensorflow/models/blob/master/research/object_detection/g3doc/detection_model_zoo.md

And it's insignificant difference when using GPU or only CPU

Input Image size for feed is 416x416 and inferenceInterface.run(outputNames, logStats); takes about ~300 ms with GPU or without GPU acceleration

body:
I'm running Object Detection https://github.com/tensorflow/models/tree/master/research/object_detection

on **ssd_inception_v2_coco** model  https://github.com/tensorflow/models/blob/master/research/object_detection/g3doc/detection_model_zoo.md

And it's insignificant difference when using GPU or only CPU

Input Image size for feed is 416x416 and `inferenceInterface.run(outputNames, logStats);` takes about ~300 ms with GPU or without GPU acceleration
